channel.title: Animation with metasequoia
channel.description:
Who thinks Metasequoia is just crap low poly modelling software?
If you got it registered, download this :- keynote - http://mqdl.jpn.org/sb.cgi?eid=18 (direct link - http://mqdl.jpn.org/img/img2_kn.lzh)
Bone.dll goes in the plugins -> command folder ExportDotX.dll goes in the plugins -> export folder MSound.dll goes in the plugins -> station folder
restart metasequoia if it's running.
load the chara.mqo from the samples.... click the new command at the bottom of the command panel. (see piccy)
Click Play - OMG
[IMG]http://i219.photobucket.com/albums/cc76/MrPotatoHead2/anim.jpg[/img]
If you want something extra stupid, get MikuMikuDance from here http://www.geocities.jp/higuchuu4/index.htm Load an example and an accessory(alt a) and click the large i-u@£|| button in the dark grey box, bottom right. Aint that so sad!!!!!
Sorry Frell - move or lock it if you want, we need a software+tut section
